1)	Provide DNA sample;
2)	Pay court costs;
3)	pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC;
4)	any other counseling, treatment, assessments as recommended by the agent;
5)	assessment, treatment, counseling as deemed appropriate by the Department's assessment process;
6)	maintain absolute sobriety; except for prescribed medications, taken in prescribed doses;
7)	Submit to random urine screens and pay for same;
8)	Maintain fulltime employment, schooling, work search or combination
